<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. وَإِنْ يَأْتِكَ الْوَسْوَاسُ يَوْماً يُشَرِّدُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>فَقَدْ أَخْبَرَ الْمُخْتَارُ يَوْماً لِصَحْبِهِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>بَأَنَّ كَثِيرَ الذِّكْرِ فِي السَّبْقِ مُفْرَدُ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَوَصَّى مُعَاذاً يَسْتَعِينُ إِلهَهُ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>عَلَى ذِكْرِهِ وَالشُّكْرِ بِالْحُسْنِ يَعْبَدُ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَأَوْصَى لِشَخْصٍ قَدْ أَتَى لِنَصِيحَةٍ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَقَدْ كَانَ فِي حَمْلِ الشَّرَائِعِ يَجْهَدُ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>بَأَنْ لا يَزَلْ رَطْْباً لِسَانُكَ هَذِهِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>تُعِينُ عَلَى كُلِّ الأُمُورِ وَتُسْعِدُ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَأَخْبَرَ أَنَّ الذِّكْرَ غَرْسٌ لأَهْلِهِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>بِجَنَّاتِ عَدْنٍ وَالْمَسَاكِنُ تُمْهَدُ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَأَخْبَرَ أَنَّ اللهَ يَذْكُرُ عَبْدَهُ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَمَعْهُ عَلَى كُلِّ الأُمُورِ يُسَدِّدُ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَأَخْبَرَ أَنَّ الذِّكْرَ يَبْقَى بِجَنَّةٍ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَيَنْقَطِعُ التَّكْلِيفُ حِينَ يُخَلَّدُ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَلَوْ لَمْ يَكُنْ فِي ذِكْرِهِ غَيْرُ أَنَّهُ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>طَرِيقٌ إِلى حُبِّ الإِلهِ وَمُرْشِدُ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَيَنْهَى الْفَتَى عَنْ غِيْبَةٍ وَنَمِيمَةٍ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَعَنْ كُلِّ قَوْلٍ لِلدِّيَانَةِ مُفْسِدُ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>